Device.Name: STM32MP13xx
Device.Description: ARM 32-bit Cortex-A7 based device, CPU clock up to 600MHz

Bit.Name: qspi_not_default_af
Bit.Description: 0:QSPI uses default hard coded AFmux 1:QSPI no default AFmux

Bit.Name: no_cpu_pll
Bit.Description: 0:PLLs for CPU/AXI are enable 1:PLLs for CPU/AXI are disable

Bit.Name: no_usb_dp_pullup
Bit.Description: 0:USB DP pull-up is set 1: USB DP pull-up is not set

Bit.Name: uart_instances_disabled
Bit.Description: Disable instance 0x1: Reserved 0x2: USART2 0x4: USART3 0x8: USART4 0x10: USART5 0x20: USART6 0x40: USART7 0x80: USART8

Bit.Name: no_data_cache
Bit.Description: 0:Data cache is used by bootrom 1:Data cache is not used by bootrom

Bit.Name: boot_source_disable
Bit.Description: Disable boot source 0x1: FMC 0x2: QSPI NOR 0x4: eMMC 0x8: SD 0x10: UART 0x20: USB 0x40: QSPI NAND

Bit.Name: HSE value
Bit.Description: 0: HSE is autodetected 1: 24 MHz 2: 25 MHz 3: 26 MHz

Bit.Name: pin0
Bit.Description: pin id between 0 and 15 for GPIOA to GPIOJ and between 0 and 7 for GPIOK and GPIOZ

Bit.Name: port0
Bit.Description: 0: Unused 1: Bank A 2: Bank B 3: Bank C 4: Bank D 5: Bank E 6: Bank F 7: Bank G 8: Bank H 9: Bank I 10-15: Unused

Bit.Name: spinand_need_plane_select
Bit.Description: 0:SPI NAND plane select not need 1:SPI NAND plane select is needed

Bit.Name: nand_nb_of_blocks
Bit.Description: Number of blocks in unit of 256 blocks

Bit.Name: nand_block_size
Bit.Description: 0:64 pages per block 1:128 pages per block 2:256 pages per block

Bit.Name: PRODUCT_BELOW_2V5
Bit.Description: Required when VDD is below 2.5 V to allow the SYSCFG high speed lowvoltage enable registers HSLVEN bits to be taken into account.

Bit.Name: TS1_FMT0
Bit.Description: DTS frequency measured freq at T0

Bit.Name: VREFINT_CAL
Bit.Description: ADC VBG measurement to correct for VREF

Bit.Name: VREFBUFTRIM
Bit.Description: 6 trim bits for each of 4 VREFBUF settings
